          .name Brilliant
          .price €5
          .trial Free 30 day trial
          hr
          ul
            li Quotes
            li
              strong Unlimited
              |         Timesheet
            li
              strong Unlimited
              |         Trip tickets
            li Directions
            li Mailing list
            li
              strong Unlimited
              |         Live chat


    .container
      h2.text-center.top-space Frequently Asked Questions
      br
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h3 Can I be updated with your new features?
          p
            | Of course! You can subscribe to our mailing list.
        .col-sm-6
          h3 Nice website. Where do I register?
          p
            | Click in the top-right button that says SIGN IN/ SIGN UP
      // /row
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h3 Can I use it to build a site for my client?
          p
            | Yes, you can. You may use this template for any purpose, just don't forget about the 
